title: Ajay Pal
text: Ajay is a passionate Biotechnologist, Fascinated by Neurodevelopmental and Neurodegenerative processes, Ajay also has a soft spot for BCI and signal encoding. Currently, he is devoted to investigating Covid19 associated neurodegeneration.
